msgctxt "Addon Summary"
msgid "Atari 7800 Proline"
msgstr "Atari 7800 Proline"

msgctxt "Addon Description"
msgid "The Atari 7800 ProSystem was released in 1986. It came bundled with the Atari Proline Joystick, but due to criticism over ergonimic issues Atari later released a gamepad with European 7800s."
msgstr "Atari 7800 ProSystem byl uveden na trh v roce 1986. Dodával se s joystickem Atari Proline, ale kvůli kritice ergonomických problémů Atari později vydalo k evropským modelům 7800 gamepad."

